en_756440_0	Colonel P.A.M Peiris assumed office as the new Commander of 212 Brigade on Thursday (15).
en_756440_1	The newly-appointed Brigade Commander was welcomed by the troops with military honours and a Guard Turnout.
en_756440_2	He succeeds Brigadier M.P Lamahewa who was appointed as the Commander, 581 Brigade.
en_756440_3	Colonel P.A.M Peiris of Sri Lanka Armoured Corps has held many important appointments during his military career in Command, Instructor and Staff appointments at various levels.
en_756440_4	Before appointing as the Commander of the 212 Brigade, Colonel P.A.M Peiris has served as the Colonel General Staff of the Security Force Headquarters (Wanni).
